                    <div class="col-2-3 m-top-100 m-bottom-300 director display">
                                                    <h1 class="text-uppercase m-top-30 m-bottom-30">
                                ICDM Protect™
                            </h1>
                                                                                                <p><img style="border: solid black 1px;" src="https://icdm.com.my/storage/membership/April2020/sterling-logo.png" width="200" height="42" /></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h4><span style="color: #1aa9e1;">ICDM Protect&trade; with Sterling Insurance Brokers</span></h4>
<p>ICDM, in partnership with Sterling Insurance Brokers, has made available the following insurance products for ICDM members only:</p>
<ul style="list-style-type: disc;">
<li>
<p><a href="#collapse1" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">Personal Directors&rsquo; and Officers&rsquo; Liability Insurance</a></p>
</li>
<li>
<p><a href="#collapse2" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">Personal Accident Insurance</a></p>
</li>
<li><a href="#collapse3" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">SmartHome All-Risks Home Insurance</a></li>
<li>
