<ul>
<li>Exclusively designed for ICDM members only to protect against potential legal liability whilst performing duty as a non-executive director of any company. You need a valid ICDM Membership for the insurance coverage.</li>
<li>Can select any three (3) companies which individual members represent for coverage purposes.</li>
<li>High policy limits.</li>
</ul>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>Competitive Premium</strong> <br />Premium ranging from RM1,320 up to RM6,400 per annum depending on the asset value of the companies which the member represents, and the limit of liability undertaken.</p>
