<h4 class="panel-title"><a href="#collapse2" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">Individual Personal Accident</a></h4>
</div>
<div id="collapse2" class="panel-collapse collapse">
<div class="panel-body">
<p><strong>Individual Personal Accident</strong> <br /><em>Underwritten by Allianz General Insurance Malaysia Berhad </em></p>
<p><strong>What is the product about?</strong> <br />This policy provides compensation in the event of injury, disability or death caused solely by accidental, external and visible events.</p>
<p><strong>What are the covers/benefits provided?</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Accidental Death;</li>
<li>Permanent Disablement;</li>
<li>24-Hour Coverage</li>
<li>Worldwide Territorial Limit</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Conditions</strong></p>
<p><strong> <em>Cash Before Cover</em> </strong> <br />The premium due must be paid and received by Allianz before the cover can commence. This coverage is automatically null and void if this condition is not satisfied.</p>
<p><strong> <em>Eligibility </em> </strong> <br />Insured Person aged between twenty one (21) years old to seventy (70) years old. <br />This insurance cover will be renewable up to seventy (70) years old</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
