<div class="panel-heading">
<h4 class="panel-title"><a href="#collapse4" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">Top-up Medical Scheme &ndash; A Health Maximiser</a></h4>
</div>
<div id="collapse4" class="panel-collapse collapse">
<div class="panel-body">
<p><strong>Top-up Medical Scheme &ndash; A Health Maximiser <br /></strong> <em>Underwritten by AIA Malaysia Berhad</em></p>
<p><strong>What is this product? <br /></strong>A Health Maximiser is a stand-alone or top-up (using the deductible value) yearly renewable medical plan exclusively designed to enhance your changing healthcare needs. Typically only given to AIA base policyholders, Sterling Insurance Brokers now allow any base policy to be topped up by AIA.</p>
<p><strong>Features of the product:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Portable and Continuous Medical Coverage
<ul>
<li>The medical plan that you can bring with you when you leave your employment and even after you retire, protecting you until age 80</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>Personalised to Your Healthcare Needs
<ul>
<li>Select from 5 attractive price plans according to your specific needs with Room and Board (between RM100 to RM500)</li>
<li>Each plan comes with two options of self-insured deductible amount</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>Full Medical Coverage upon Retirement
<ul>
<li>At age 60, this self-insured deductible amount shall be reduced to zero and you shall enjoy full medical coverage from the first Ringgit of claims</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>Option to Protect Your Loved Ones
<ul>
<li>Your spouse and children can also enjoy the benefits offered by this product</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>Cashless Hospital Admission with Letter of Guarantee
<ul>
<li>The product provides you hassle-free admission with just a phone call &ndash; 1300 8888 60 / 70 for issuance of Letter of Guarantee to all panel hospitals</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
